description:
This is a 16 minute workout called 'BEST BEGINNER Tread Workout for 15 MINUTES' from the channel IBX Running.
The workout falls under Cardio/Treadmill and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Treadmill for this workout.
The workout has a The Meditative Grind and The Endorphin Wave vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light and Moderate.

Original workout description: We are back after a week break and we missed you! Coming at you with the BEST Beginner 15 minute tread run on YouTube! Come get sweaty!

15:00 minutes of run and recovery intervals

All speeds and inclines are suggestions. Please stay safe and within your comfort zone!

Join this channel to get access to perks:

00:00 - Intro
00:37 - Warm Up
02:38 - Workout!
13:05 - Cool Down
